divs: Sighting DetailsLast summer the space station flew over chicago at the time indicated. Not knowing what to see I was looking for any thing that moved. My house faces south, in my frt. yard I look up and saw a star like object moving at a good speed. I thought this was it and came back in then I saw the time was off so I went back out and saw the real shuttle go over head. The news media interviewed a man who had pictures of the object(three orbs) but that was the end of the interview. The station was abc 7 or nbc 5. This has troubled me as to what I saw. The star object I saw was so farr away all it looked lkie was a star but not a shooting star. This one moved left to right in a Z patteren and went out of sight.
Summary: Space shuttle fly over and a sighting.
